== 衛生問題 ==
燒味店的衛生狀況一直為人詬病，由於大部分燒味店位處[[街市|街市]]或路邊，其周邊的環境不甚清潔。加上，一般燒味都是掛在店內展示，增加暴露於空氣接觸病菌的風險。<ref name="S">{{cite news|url=http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2020/0304/422260.html|title=﻿燒味師傅邊斬邊收錢 隨時播毒|work=[[大公報|大公報]]|date=2020-03-04|accessdate=2021-08-25|archive-date=2021-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825191502/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2020/0304/422260.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而店舖東主亦經常一邊斬切燒味，一邊交收現金，途中鮮有清潔雙手，亦增加食物安全風險。<ref name="S" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201013/s00001/1602580049833/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%87%92%E5%91%B3%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%AC%E6%96%99%E6%94%B6%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E5%80%A1%E8%A8%AD%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2-%E5%94%94%E9%A9%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A|title=燒味店一人斬料收錢包裝　袁國勇倡設針對措施　顧客：唔驚得咁多|work=[[明報|明報]]|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2021-08-25|archive-date=2021-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210917091151/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201013/s00001/1602580049833/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%87%92%E5%91%B3%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%AC%E6%96%99%E6%94%B6%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E5%80%A1%E8%A8%AD%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2-%E5%94%94%E9%A9%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A|dead-url=no}}</ref>

